Enkare natupukuo te ndapidapoi

(Enki 
20  .
1  -
13  )


1  Nepuo olturrur pooki loo Siraeli to lpurkel le Sini too lkirragarien, anaa enaitanapa Olaitoriani, neitayu ilng'oborri te Refidim; kake metii apa enkare naok iltung'ana. 
2  Neilepilepaki iltung'ana Musa, nejo, “Nchoo iyiook enkare nikiok.” Nejoki Musa ninche, “Kainyoo pee kilepilepakiki nanu? Kainyoo pee itemiteme Olaitoriani?” 
3  Kake etotiro iltung'ana enkure oleng, neing'unyung'unyaki iltung'ana Musa, nejo, “Kainyoo apa pee iyaua iyiook aaitung'uaa Misiri, nilotu aar iyiook matuata o nkera ang o nkishu ang te nkure?” 
4  Neishiraki Musa Olaitoriani nejo, “Kaa aitaas kulo tung'ana? Etaa ninche kejo pee aanang too soito.” 
5  Nejoki Olaitoriani Musa, “Togiroi iltung'ana te dukuya, nishoroo te nebo iyie embata oo lpayiani loo Siraeli; niya te nkaina ino ina ng'udi apa nitooshie olkeju le Nail, nilo. 
6  Ng'ura kalo nanu aitashe te dukuya iyie te idie te nchumata e ndapidapoi te Horeb, niosh iyie ina dapidapoi, naa kepuku enkare ti atua ninye, pee etum iltung'ana aatook.” Neas Musa ina te dukuya ilpayiani loo Siraeli. 
7  Nejo ninye enkarna eine wueji Masa o Meriba, te nkaraki enkilepilep oo ltung'ana loo Siraeli, o enkaraki natetema ninche Olaitoriani ejo. “Ketii Olaitoriani te nebo iyiook arashu metii?”

Olarrabal te nebo Ilmaleki


8  Neitoki Amalek alotu nearare Isiraeli te Refidim. 
9  Nejoki Musa Yoshua, “Tegelaki iyiook ilewa, nimpang'ipang'a aapuo, entaarata o Amalek; ore taisere naitashe nanu te nchumata e ndoinyo aata ina ng'udi e Nkai te nkaina ai.” 
10  Neas Yoshua enatiaaka Musa, nearare Amalek; nelo Musa o Aron o Huri enchumata e ndoinyo. 
11  Ore ake te neilepie Musa enkaina, nemirisho Isiraeli, ore ake te neitadou enkaina enye, nemirisho Ilmaleki. 
12  Kake etanaurate inkaik e Musa, neyau ninche osoit nepik abori ninye, netonie ninye nedumu Aron o Huri inkaik enyena aailepie, obo ake te nchoto nabo o likae ti ae shoto; metaa keitirring'a eitoriori inkaik enyena o metadoi enkolong. 
13  Nemir Yoshua aitadoyio Ilmaleki o ltung'ana lenyena neshurt te nepi o lalem.


14   Nejoki Olaitoriani Musa, “Ing'ero ena te mbuku metaa endamunoto niliki Yoshua ajoki ekamut nanu aimisie endamunoto oo Ilmaleki aiwuang'ie ti abori keper.” 
15  Neshetu Musa olperere lo lasar nejo enkarna enye, Olaitoriani ninye enanka ai 
16  ejo, “Einosa Olaitoriani olmumai nchere kearare ninye Ilmaleki ebaiki eishoi o eishoi.”

